'''Karekezi Uwacu Martine''' yabaye umwanditsi ukomeye  w’[[Igitabo|ibitabo]] abitewe no kubura inkuru akoresha yigisha [[abana]].<ref>https://igihe.com/dusangire-ijambo/article/uko-karekezi-martine-yabaye-umwanditsi-w-ibitabo-abitewe-no-kubura-inkuru</ref> '''Uwacu Karekezi Martine''' avuga ko kwandika [[Igitabo|ibitabo]] no gushushanya atari impano [[Imana]] iha abagabo bonyine, gusa haracyari [[Umugore|abagore]] benshi babikora bakabiherana mu [[Urugo rwa Yezu Nyirimpuhwe mu Ruhango|ngo]] zabo, n'abatabona uko bakoresha impano yabo, nyamara uyu ni umwuga urimo imibereho.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-53691693</ref>

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Uwacu Karekezi Martine''', ni umwarimukazi<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/latest-news/new-book-cautions-people-incestuous-violence</ref> w’[[Indimi mu kinyarwanda|indimi]] wabigize umwuga wigisha [[abana]] bo mu [[Ishuri|mashuri]] y’incuke kuri [https://greenhillsacademy.rw/ Green Hills Academy],<ref>https://greenhillsacademy.rw/</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/latest-news/new-book-cautions-people-incestuous-violence</ref> mu [[Umujyi wa Kigali|Mujyi wa Kigali]]. Hejuru yo kuba umwarimukazi<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/latest-news/new-book-cautions-people-incestuous-violence</ref>, ni umwanditsi w’[[Igitabo|ibitabo]] by’[[abana]],<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/latest-news/new-book-cautions-people-incestuous-violence</ref> imivugo, gushushanya n’ibindi bifite aho bihuriye n’ubugeni.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/latest-news/new-book-cautions-people-incestuous-violence</ref> Uyu mwarimu umaze [[imyaka]] isaga 15 mu [[Uburezi mu Rwanda|uburezi]], yavuze ko agitangira kwigisha yaje kujya ahura n’ikibazo cy’inkuru ziryoshye zijyanye n’amasomo yabaga asabwa kwigisha[[Ishuri|abanyeshuri]] be. Yarebye kujya apfa [[Kwigisha english-kinyarwanda|kwigisha]] uko abonye, abona yaba ari gutatira amahame agenga umwuga w’[[Uburezi mu Rwanda|uburezi]], ahitamo gutangira kwiyandikira inkuru zizajya zijyana n’amasomo ashaka kwigisha [[abana]].<ref>https://igihe.com/dusangire-ijambo/article/uko-karekezi-martine-yabaye-umwanditsi-w-ibitabo-abitewe-no-kubura-inkuru</ref>

== KWANDIKA IBITABO ==
'''Karekezi Uwacu Martine''' avuga ko aka [[Akazi Kanoze (AKA)|akazi]] ko kwa ndika [[Igitabo|ibitabo]], yagatangiye  agitangira  kwigisha [[abana]]. Hari ukuntu ukenera kwigisha [[abana]] isomo, ukabona nta nkuru n’[[Rimwe|imwe]] iri mu [[igitabo]] ufite yagufasha kwigisha [[abana]].”Yakomeje agira ati “Njye ntabwo inkuru nari nkeneye byari ngombwa ko ziba mu [[Igitabo|bitabo]] cyangwa ngo zimpe amafaranga, nta nubwo nari nzi ko hari uwazikunda ngo azishyire mu [[Igitabo|ibitabo]] ariko njye zari zinyuze n’[[Ishuri|abanyeshuri]] banjye zikabaryohera. Nkandika inkuru yarangiza ibyo nayihimbiye nkayishyira mu kabati nkayibika.”<ref>https://womxn-artists.rw/artists/karekezi-uwacu-martine/</ref>

Mu [[Imyaka|imwaka]] wa 2015, Uwacu yaje guhura n’abashinzwe guteza imbere ibijyanye n’[[Igitabo|ibitabo]] mu muryango [https://rwanda.savethechildren.net/ Save the Children]<ref>https://rwanda.savethechildren.net/</ref>, bamusangana [[Igitabo|agatabo]] gato yari yariyandikiye n’intoki karimo [[Rimwe|imwe]] mu inkuru yajyaga yifashisha yigisha [[Ishuri|abanyeshuri]] be. Ako [[Igitabo|gatabo]] baragakunze, bamwizeza kumuhuza n’[[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|inzu]] zisohora [[Igitabo|ibitabo]] zikomeye zikamufasha gushyira hanze inkuru ze. Ati “Bampuje n[[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|’inzu]] zisohora [[Igitabo|ibitabo]] ndetse n’abashushanya, bakunda inkuru zanjye uyikunze akambwira ko ayigura.”<ref>https://igihe.com/dusangire-ijambo/article/uko-karekezi-martine-yabaye-umwanditsi-w-ibitabo-abitewe-no-kubura-inkuru</ref> Mu [[imyaka]] mike amaze atangiye gusohora [[Igitabo|ibitabo]], amaze gusohora [[Igitabo|ibitabo]] 20 birimo inkuru z’[[abana]] ndetse n’ibindi bine birimo [[Umuvungovungo|imivugo]]. Avuga ko amafaranga ava mu bwanditsi bw’[[Igitabo|ibitabo]] ataraba menshi nk’uko bikwiriye ariko ku muntu wakuze akunda kwandika ibyo bitamuca intege. Ati “Abantu bandika ibyishimo bya mbere ntabwo ari amafaranga. Inyungu ya mbere tugira ni ukubona ko hari abasomye ibyo twanditse cyangwa se akaguha igitekerezo gitandukanye. Uguhaye igitekerezo aba aguhaye inyungu iruta uwari kukigura akagishyira mu akabati.” '''Uwacu''' nyuma yo gushyira hanze impano ze, yashinze [https://vymaps.com/RW/Sankofa-Creatives-Ltd-317773278832874/ Sankofa Creative Ltd]<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/young-rwandan-visual-artist-wins-africalia-grants</ref><ref>https://vymaps.com/RW/Sankofa-Creatives-Ltd-317773278832874/</ref>, [[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|inzu]] ihuriza hamwe abahanzi n’ abanyabugeni mu ngeri zitandukanye, bagahanga, bagakosorana bakagurisha.

Ubwanditsi bwatumye '''Uwacu''' atagihorana umutima uhangayitse, cyangwa se ngo ahore arambirije ku mushahara gusa.

